&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;WORCESTERSHIRE ACUTE HOSPITALS NHS TRUST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;WORCESTERSHIRE ROYAL HOSPITAL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;OUT OF HOURS DOCTOR (Equivalent to DCT2/CT1 Level) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;ORAL &amp; MAXILLOFACIAL SURGERY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are recruiting for Out of Hours Doctors (Equivalent to DCT2/3 level) to commence immediately for a period of 12 months in the first instance. The post will be based at Worcestershire Royal Hospital and will provide resident on call cover for the department of maxillofacial surgery. Candidates will have experience at DCT2/3 level or equivalent. Candidates should hold the BDS or equivalent and ideally the MFDS or equivalent. The positions are ideally suited to candidates studying for their undergraduate medical degree prior to entry to specialist maxillofacial training. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;During the period as post-holder you will be part of maxillofacial surgery on-call surgical team. Your responsibility will be to take acute referrals of patients with maxillofacial conditions and to look after the maxillofacial surgery in-patients. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The hours of duty will include 1900 – 0700 (nights) and 0700 to 1900 weekends (long days). A handover will be expected at the beginning and end of the shift.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Informal enquiries of a clinical nature should be made to Mr K McVeigh, Consultant Oral &amp; Maxillofacial Surgeon on 01905 733020.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
